General Information

David Craig's Skincare range comprises both ready to use creams and ointments which are readily available for use by consumers, as well as a comprehensive range of products used for extemporaneous preparations, which are often used to treat acute skin or medical conditions. All David Craig skincare products are stringently quality tested and are produced in a high quality GMP facility.

Warnings

Store below 30°C

Ingredients

100% Pure petroleum jelly

Directions

Extemporaneous preparations: Use as required to make various creams, ointments and lotions.
